name: ROCKETBOOTS - PROTOTYPE
description:
Welcome to ROCKETBOOTS.

WASD + Space to move.

Click to use your ROCKETBOOTS. They will fling you in whatever direction you are facing.

Your ROCKETBOOTS recharge whenever you land on the ground or on a boost pad.

Your goal is to reach the sky beam in as little time as possible.

Go get 'em, champ.
